1
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:08,641
Meeting Highlights is a new Microsoft Teams feature that delivers a dynamic, bite-sized video recap of your meeting, typically 3 to 5 minutes long.

2
00:00:09,841 --> 00:00:17,521
It uses AI to automatically identify and stitch together the most important moments from your Teams meetings, creating an engaging highlights video.

3
00:00:18,802 --> 00:00:26,882
The feature combines AI-generated voiceover summaries with authentic video snippets from the actual meeting, preserving the original tone, reactions, and flow.

4
00:00:27,882 --> 00:00:35,362
Users can access Meeting Highlights through Microsoft 365 Copilot, Teams Recap, and other M365 entry points after a meeting is recorded.

5
00:00:36,362 --> 00:00:44,842
The video includes subtitles for accessibility and allows users to navigate between highlight segments, making it easy to jump to specific topics of interest.

6
00:00:45,842 --> 00:00:53,322
This solves a critical problem: catching up on missed meetings without watching hour-long recordings or reading lengthy transcripts.

7
00:00:54,322 --> 00:01:02,802
Internal users have called it magical, with over 80% rating it as extremely useful or very useful, and 96% likely to use it again.

8
00:01:03,802 --> 00:01:11,282
The feature is currently in preview for enterprise customers with Microsoft 365 Copilot licenses, with general availability planned for 2024.